     <div class="row less3 novrflw"> 
      <div class="span4 grybx"> 
       <h4>OP Staff</h4> 
       <div class="flt-left">
        <a href="#"><img alt="${image.getChild('title').value}" src="_images/Durell_121005_UCOP_office_0682.jpg"></a>
       </div> 
       <p>Find the latest news and resources just for OP employees. </p> 
       <ul class="prp-dots"> 
        <li><a href="/navigating-ucop/resources/index.html">Navigating UCOP</a></li> 
        <li><a href="http://link.ucop.edu" target="_blank">Link newsletter</a></li> 
        <li><a href="/staff-assembly/index.html">OP Staff Assembly</a></li> 
       </ul> 
      </div> 
      <div class="span4 grybx"> 
       <h4>UCnet &amp; At Your Service Online</h4> 
       <p><a href="http://ucnet.universityofcalifornia.edu">UCnet</a> is a systemwide website for UC faculty, staff and retirees, providing news, information about benefits and policies and access to a wealth of tools and resources.</p> 
       <p>You can also log on to your employee accounts at <a href="https://atyourserviceonline.ucop.edu/ayso/">At Your Service Online</a>.</p> 
      </div> 
      <div class="span4 grybx"> 
       <h4>What's new?</h4> 
       <div class="flt-left">
        <a href="#"><img alt="${image.getChild('title').value}" src="_images/star.png"></a>
       </div> 
       <p>The <strong>STAR Program</strong> (Staff Appreciation and Recognition Plan)&nbsp;allows managers to give one-time cash awards to staff in recognition of exemplary performance and contributions.</p> 
       <p><a href="op-life/employee-recognition/star-program.html">Learn more and nominate a UCOP employee!</a></p> 
      </div> 
